Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*外面的天气真可怕*\N{\fs38}*Oh, the weather outside is frightful*
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞快乐\N{\fs38}Merry Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给每一个人都织了袜子\N{\fs38}I made everyone stockings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lillian{\fs38}\NLillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:10.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Titus{\fs38}\NTitus.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己\N{\fs38}Yours truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.84,0:00:12.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mimi{\fs38}\NMimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.96,0:00:14.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有Murasaki\N{\fs38}And Murasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:16.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Murasaki不过圣诞节\N{\fs38}Murasaki doesn't do Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.51,0:00:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 我爱圣诞节\N{\fs38}Gosh, I love Christmas:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.05,0:00:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着音乐 拆开礼物\N{\fs38}the music, untangling things,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.85,0:00:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在室外张灯结彩 在室内布置圣诞树\N{\fs38}putting lights outdoors and trees indoors.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有什么\N{\fs38}Say what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.97,0:00:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们欢聚一堂 为如此多美好的事情庆祝\N{\fs38}And we're all together with so much to celebrate:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.02,0:00:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非同一般的友谊和全新的人生冒险\N{\fs38}special friendships and new adventures
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.35,0:00:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后再说一句 "再见"\N{\fs38}and giving a final "Later, gator"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让烦恼属于过往\N{\fs38}to the problems of yester--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗝往\N{\fs38}Yester-- urp.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听到了\N{\fs38}You heard me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.03,0:00:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 你应该去看医生\N{\fs38}Honey, you should see a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.28,0:00:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这味道好像是你体内死了一只老鼠\N{\fs38}It's like a mouse died in the walls of your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.91,0:00:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗬 嗬 嗬\N{\fs38}Ho, ho, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你们所有人圣诞快乐\N{\fs38}Merry Christmas to all of youse!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.87,0:00:48.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞老人\N{\fs38}Santa?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.37,0:00:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣诞老人\N{\fs38}Santa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能亲吻你 我已经结婚了\N{\fs38}Oh, I can't kiss you. I'm married.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.13,0:00:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些犹太人夺走了我的画\N{\fs38}The Jews took my painting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.01,0:00:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在才是真正的派对\N{\fs38}Now it's a party.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.05,0:01:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗬 嗬 嗬 你这个贱人\N{\fs38}Ho, ho, ho. You ho.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.43,0:01:03.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sonja{\fs38}\NSonja?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要杀了你\N{\fs38}I'm gonna kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.18,屏字,NTP,0,0,0,,{\c&H65D9F5&\pos(640,300.667)}三 个 月 前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.73,0:01:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件破事发生之前的三个月\N{\fs38}Three months earlier on this mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.40,0:01:11.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自从我看到这家店的名字叫"迷你汉堡"\N{\fs38}I've been wanting to bring you to this place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.77,0:01:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就一直想带你来\N{\fs38}ever since I saw it was called Sliderz.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.77,0:01:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我要向你道歉\N{\fs38}I apologize, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.90,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,店名Sliderz意为迷你汉堡 同时slides有滑梯的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实这里并没有任何"滑梯"\N{\fs38}There aren't actually any slides in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.99,0:01:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是看看这些迷你汉堡\N{\fs38}But look at these tiny hamburgers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.36,0:01:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们使你感觉像个巨人\N{\fs38}They make you feel like a giant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.07,0:01:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要一口吃掉你\N{\fs38}I'm gonna eat you up in one bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.12,0:01:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"求求你 不要吃我 我还有家人"\N{\fs38}"Please, no, I have a family."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.62,0:01:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这太有意思了 Kimmy\N{\fs38}This is so fun, Kimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴我逃离了我的绿卡婚姻\N{\fs38}I'm so glad I ran away from my green card marriage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续跟你约会\N{\fs38}to go on dates with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.87,0:01:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是素食主义者\N{\fs38}I'm a vegan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 你刚才说什么\N{\fs38}Wait, what did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 "我是素食主义者"\N{\fs38}I said, "I'm a vegan."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.09,0:01:35.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为当我们在5公里动物权益公益跑\N{\fs38}I thought you knew that
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.10,0:01:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相遇的时候 你就已经知道这件事了\N{\fs38}when we met at that animal rights 5K.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为那活动是为了让动物们可以自由结婚\N{\fs38}Oh, I thought that was so animals could marry each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这次约会进展得\N{\fs38}Well, I think this date is going...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.60,0:01:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好讨厌\N{\fs38}Hated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.18,0:01:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这很困难 是因为\N{\fs38}Oh, it's hard because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.27,0:01:50.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还跟你的前任藕断丝连\N{\fs38}you're still hung up on your ex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.73,0:01:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能理解\N{\fs38}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还会回想起我的初恋 Bobby\N{\fs38}I still think about my first love, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.02,0:01:59.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经一起参加罗斯福岛的夏令营\N{\fs38}We went to summer camp together on Roosevelt Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.53,0:02:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小Bobby Durst\N{\fs38}Little Bobby Durst.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.61,0:02:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为他倾倒\N{\fs38}He was my first crush.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.70,0:02:05.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是字面意思 他想要击倒我\N{\fs38}Literally, he tried to crush me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.99,0:02:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等了15年才重新恢复自己的生活\N{\fs38}It's just, I waited 15 years to get my life back,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:10.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后来我找到了工作 找到了男朋友\N{\fs38}and then I got a job, I got a boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.96,0:02:13.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这个世界好像在对我说 "你神经病啊"\N{\fs38}but then the world was like, "Psych!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我理解 亲爱的 你现在就想得到全部\N{\fs38}I know, dear, you want it all right now:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美满事业 如意郎君\N{\fs38}the career, the husband,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.13,0:02:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有泪滴纹身\N{\fs38}the teardrop tattoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.59,0:02:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 先去寻欢作乐吧\N{\fs38}But hey, have a little fun for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我带你出去\N{\fs38}Hey, let me take you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.56,0:02:29.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是撩汉好队友\N{\fs38}Ooh, I'm a great wingman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.93,0:02:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人们发现我非常容易亲近\N{\fs38}Men find me very approachable
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我有一双大眼睛\N{\fs38}because my eyes are large
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.44,0:02:35.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我的头发长得像好看的意面\N{\fs38}and my hair is like beautiful spaghetti.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以把他们钓上钩\N{\fs38}I get 'em on the hook.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.19,0:02:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我们悄悄地在饮料里下摇头丸\N{\fs38}Then we'll slip 'em a disco biscuit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再偷偷地把饮料换给他们\N{\fs38}and pull a switcheroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.82,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,双关: Timberlake曾是男子组合NSYNC的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.57,0:02:44.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟上我的步伐 Kimberlake 我要去离婚\N{\fs38}Get 'NSYNC, Kimberlake. I got to go get divorced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.91,0:02:47.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我们要大肆狂欢\N{\fs38}Oh, we're gonna paint the town red tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个问题\N{\fs38}Ooh, two questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:52.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢西班牙小伙子吗 还有 你会滑旱冰吗\N{\fs38}Do you like Spanish guys, and can you roller-skate?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢 只接受正面体位\N{\fs38}Yes, but only frontways.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.33,0:02:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会吧\N{\fs38}And probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.54,0:02:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 我说的是"可能喜欢 只会向前滑"\N{\fs38}Oh, wait, I said that backwards.
