Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的房子在那边 呆子\N{\fs38}Hey, your house is that way, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.92,0:03:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天啊 谢谢你\N{\fs38}Oh, my God, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.67,0:03:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经站在这里好几个小时了\N{\fs38}I've been standing here for hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.92,0:03:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心点 我在那边拉了粑粑\N{\fs38}Watch out. I pooped over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据Wilkerson太太提供的证书\N{\fs38}So, according to the license presented by Mrs. Wilkerson,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:54.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们俩是在1998年6月6日结婚的\N{\fs38}you two were married on June 6, 1998.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.64,0:03:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也能叫结婚\N{\fs38}Barely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.35,0:03:58.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ronald Ephen Wilkerson 你是否愿意\N{\fs38}And do you, Ronald Ephen Wilkerson,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,娶这位女子为你的合法妻子\N{\fs38}take this woman to be your lawfully wedded wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs38}Mm-kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且Wilkerson太太声称你在1998年6月6日\N{\fs38}And Mrs. Wilkerson claims that you abandoned her
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抛弃了她\N{\fs38}on June 6, 1998.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下\N{\fs38}Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.16,0:04:12.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是同一天\N{\fs38}That's the same day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.45,0:04:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 我不清楚\N{\fs38}Is it? I wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你甚至在我们跳第一支舞之前就离开了\N{\fs38}You left before we even did our first dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.96,0:04:18.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且你知道我们的编舞非常完美\N{\fs38}And you know our choreography was on point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.33,0:04:19.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有一次能接住我\N{\fs38}Mm, you dropped me every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.96,0:04:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为你至少是跟一个男的跑了\N{\fs38}I thought at least you ran away to be with a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.59,0:04:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你却在这里\N{\fs38}But here you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.84,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占一个傻女孩的便宜\N{\fs38}taking advantage of some other goofy girl
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.55,0:04:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她穿得像个他妈的史酷比狗\N{\fs38}dressed like she's on Scooby damn Doo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.64,0:04:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没想到啊 Ronald\N{\fs38}I can't believe you, Ronald.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要叫我Ronald\N{\fs38}Do not call me Ronald.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Rah-nald\N{\fs38}Rah-nald.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为你可以安然无恙地脱身吗\N{\fs38}You think you can walk away from your problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我找到你了\N{\fs38}Well, I found you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.48,0:04:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要起诉你 要求你赔偿17年的配偶赡养费\N{\fs38}and I'm gonna sue you for 17 years' worth of spousal support,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.19,0:04:45.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有400美元的婚礼费用\N{\fs38}$400 for the wedding itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.19,0:04:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还要拿回我的新娘外套\N{\fs38}and I want my bridal jacket back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要夺走你所拥有的一切 Ronald Wilkerson\N{\fs38}I'm gonna take everything you got, Ronald Wilkerson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.95,0:04:54.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 Titus\N{\fs38}Really, Titus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还要再逃一次吗\N{\fs38}You're just gonna run away from her again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.00,0:04:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说蒙特利尔有一个充满活力的戏剧舞台\N{\fs38}I hear Montreal has a vibrant theater scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.54,0:05:00.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了 亲爱的\N{\fs38}so au revoir, les Felicieuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许去和Vonda谈一下就好了\N{\fs38}Maybe just go talk to Vonda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你完全没和她说过话 你们可是夫妻哎\N{\fs38}You haven't spoken to her at all, and you guys were married.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kim 你不明白\N{\fs38}Kim, you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说 密西西比州就是一个坑\N{\fs38}Mississippi was my bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.05,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,摩奇: 一种新型有机覆盖物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从周一开始忙活Vonda她舅舅的摩奇生意\N{\fs38}I start work Monday at Vonda's uncle's mulch business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs38}What's that you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我从周一开始忙活Vonda她舅舅的摩奇生意\N{\fs38}I said I start work Monday at Vonda's uncle's mulch business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥\N{\fs38}What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从周一开始 忙活Vonda她舅舅的摩奇生意\N{\fs38}I start work Monday... at Vonda's uncle's mulch business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 亲爱的\N{\fs38}What, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.48,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说我是一个恐慌症发作的同性恋\N{\fs38}I said I'm a homosexual having a panic attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.78,0:05:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这岂不是美妙极了\N{\fs38}Oh, isn't that wonderful?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来\N{\fs38}And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.91,0:05:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们欢迎这对新人到舞池中央来\N{\fs38}please welcome to the dance floor
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.41,0:05:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们将开启人生中的第二个也是最后一个阶段\N{\fs38}as they begin this second and final part of their lives,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:39.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请Ronald Wilkerson夫妇\N{\fs38}Mr. And Mrs. Ronald Wilkerson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.84,0:05:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不就是Ronald Wilkerson吗\N{\fs38}Aren't you Ronald Wilkerson?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.67,0:05:46.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是说我吗 不是 先生\N{\fs38}Who me? No, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是\N{\fs38}I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Titus Andromedon{\fs38}\NTitus Andromedon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ronald Wilkerson 请你现身\N{\fs38}Ronald Wilkerson, show your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:58.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我鼓起了最大的勇气去逃跑\N{\fs38}It took all the courage I had to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.02,0:06:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Titus使我避免了那种除了小孩就是摩奇的生活\N{\fs38}Titus saved me from a life of babies and mulch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.73,0:06:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在Vonda要夺走我所创造的美好世界\N{\fs38}Now Vonda's gonna take away this beautiful world I built for my--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的蠹虫\N{\fs38}Damn silverfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.53,0:06:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我去跟Vonda谈呢\N{\fs38}What if I go talk to Vonda?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许我可以打动她\N{\fs38}Maybe I could get through to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是两个女人之间的交流\N{\fs38}woman to woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.28,0:06:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恶\N{\fs38}Ew.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带她出去吃冰淇淋\N{\fs38}I'll take her out for ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有甜筒在手上总不会生气了吧\N{\fs38}You can't be mad with a cone in your paw.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 但是以防万一 我要继续收拾东西\N{\fs38}Okay, but just in case, I'm gonna keep on packing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.95,0:06:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少也要等到我的血糖降下来\N{\fs38}at least until my blood sugar drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.25,0:06:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,降了降了\N{\fs38}There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.79,0:06:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们在这里向我们之中的一员表示祝贺\N{\fs38}We are here today to celebrate one of our own,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.09,0:06:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anthony Black Elk\N{\fs38}Anthony Black Elk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将在几天后去达特茅斯学院上学\N{\fs38}who's going away to Dartmouth College in a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要去当傻逼曲棍球运动员\N{\fs38}Don't become some d-bag lacrosse player.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亲爱的 是我们发明了曲棍球\N{\fs38}Honey, we invented lacrosse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能认同\N{\fs38}I don't think that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Anthony 这神圣的烟斗\N{\fs38}Anthony, this sacred pipe,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.31,0:06:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名叫chanunpa\N{\fs38}the chanunpa,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.23,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是九代之前雕刻成的\N{\fs38}was carved nine generations ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它在翁迪德尼战役中幸存了下来\N{\fs38}It survived Wounded Knee,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.65,0:06:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们曾经用它来为越南战争中的兄弟们祈祷\N{\fs38}and we used it to pray for our brothers in Vietnam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而今天我们将呼唤伟大的神灵\N{\fs38}And today we will ask the Great Spirit--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这他妈的是什么\N{\fs38}What the holy hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是电子烟 爸爸\N{\fs38}It's a tobacco vape, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.37,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Katherine Heigl: 美国女演员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.41,0:07:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Katherine Heigl也抽这烟\N{\fs38}Katherine Heigl uses one.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸烟有害健康啊 各位\N{\fs38}Smoking kills, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:06.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神圣烟斗在哪里 Jackie Lynn\N{\fs38}Where is that pipe, Jackie Lynn?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把烟斗举在空中 它被一只鹰叼走了\N{\fs38}I held it in the air, and a hawk took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jackie Lynn\N{\fs38}Jackie Lynn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 烟斗在棋盘游戏后面的壁橱里\N{\fs38}Oh, fine, it's in the hall closet behind the board games.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老烟枪\N{\fs38}Addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.64,0:07:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁在那里\N{\fs38}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.72,0:07:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jackie Lynn 戴上你的隐形眼镜吧\N{\fs38}Jackie Lynn, just use your contact lenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.06,0:07:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你需要按照医生的处方去做\N{\fs38}You need the prescription.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 妈妈\N{\fs38}No, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.35,0:07:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们会使我的眼睛变蓝的\N{\fs38}They turn my eyes blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.81,0:07:29.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他们通过飞行射击游戏和对口型大作战\N{\fs38}And that's me giving in to white culture,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使我向白人文化屈服\N{\fs38}with their drone wars and lip-sync battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.32,0:07:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就买没有颜色的嘛\N{\fs38}Well, then order plain ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我看到你在给雄野牛挤奶\N{\fs38}Yesterday I saw you try to milk a male buffalo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.49,0:07:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 妈妈\N{\fs38}Whatever, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挤出来了 放到冰箱里了\N{\fs38}It worked. I put it in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你准备什么时候\N{\fs38}And when are you gonna
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.29,0:07:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你开来的那辆警车还回去\N{\fs38}give back that police car you showed up in?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面住着一只浣熊\N{\fs38}There's a raccoon living in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.29,0:07:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它已经死了\N{\fs38}Oh, he's not living in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.88,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,原理同儿童锁\N
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囚犯锁起了作用 它被关在了警车后面\N{\fs38}He got stuck in the back because of the prisoner locks
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后它中暑死了\N{\fs38}and he died of heatstroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你是好心\N{\fs38}I know you mean well,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.01,0:07:57.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但不要再来帮忙了\N{\fs38}but just stop trying to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我想帮忙\N{\fs38}But I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想尽到自己\N{\fs38}All I want is to be the daughter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作为女儿的本分\N{\fs38}I should have been this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.39,0:08:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉我我能做什么 我不会让你们失望的\N{\fs38}Just tell me what I can do, and I won't let you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证\N{\fs38}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 你可以走远一点 到田地去\N{\fs38}Well, you could go far, far in the fields
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去跳超级特别而且非常重要的丰收舞蹈\N{\fs38}and do the harvest super special important dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.65,0:08:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来好重要\N{\fs38}That sounds important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会教你怎么跳\N{\fs38}I'll teach it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.12,0:08:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见\N{\fs38}Aloha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:30.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}Oh, Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:33.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我之所以打电话叫你出来\N{\fs38}Look, the reason I called
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.17,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为Titus 讨厌\N{\fs38}is 'cause Titus-- Dang!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快舔干净\N{\fs38}Lick it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.30,0:08:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么事吗\N{\fs38}What's your deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.59,0:08:39.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你简直就像个卡通人物\N{\fs38}You're like a cartoon person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:44.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话 我不是真的想要Ronald的钱\N{\fs38}Honestly, I don't even really want money from Ronald.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想让他道歉\N{\fs38}I just want him to apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.19,0:08:48.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样做可能会使我看上去像个傻瓜 Kimmy\N{\fs38}This might make me seem like a fool, Kimmy,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们曾爱过彼此\N{\fs38}but we loved each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我们曾经爱过\N{\fs38}I know we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说 我早就知道他喜欢男人\N{\fs38}I mean, I knew he liked men.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.24,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Tim Meadows: 美国黑人男演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.69,0:08:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有请Tim Meadows\N{\fs38}With Tim Meadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:08:59.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是他也知道我喜欢苗条的白人小子\N{\fs38}But he knew I liked skinny white boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.58,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,David Spade: 美国白人男演员
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.78,0:09:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,David Spade{\fs38}\N...David Spade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:07.83,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Hootie & the Blowfish: 男子音乐组合 成员有白人有黑人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.66,0:09:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音乐表演嘉宾 Hootie & the Blowfish\N{\fs38}Musical guest: Hootie & the Blowfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都无法在奇克索县做真实的自己\N{\fs38}Neither of us could live our truth in Chickasaw County.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.50,0:09:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想 "我们将一起生活在谎言之中"\N{\fs38}So I thought, "We gonna live our lie together."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:18.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那天晚上 我们婚礼那天晚上\N{\fs38}But that night, our wedding night,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当大家意识到Ronald已经逃走了的时候\N{\fs38}when they realized Ronald ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.97,0:09:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抚养他长大成人的五个姑妈\N{\fs38}every one of his five aunties that raised him
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.68,0:09:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,统统都心脏病发作了\N{\fs38}had a heart attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.85,0:09:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将我抛弃在舞池中 我独自一人\N{\fs38}And he left me on that dance floor, alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别无选择 只好一路跳着机械舞回到了车里\N{\fs38}with no choice but to Robocop my way to the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太糟糕了\N{\fs38}That's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:40.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ronald Wilkerson永远不会对我做那种事\N{\fs38}Ronald Wilkerson would have never done that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的朋友Titus干的\N{\fs38}That was your friend Titus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.58,0:09:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我甚至都认不出他来了\N{\fs38}I don't even recognize that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎样 他确实填充过脸颊 不过失败了\N{\fs38}For what it's worth, he did get cheek implants that slipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会重蹈我的覆辙\N{\fs38}You're the new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看现在的你 还在想办法收拾他的烂摊子\N{\fs38}Look at you right now, trying to clean up his mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦你变得对他没有利用价值\N{\fs38}But once there's nothing else that Titus can get from you,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.30,0:09:57.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就会甩下一张待付的牙医账单和满满一冰箱\N{\fs38}he will leave you with an unpaid dental bill
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.80,0:10:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变质了的婚宴虾仁 然后离你而去\N{\fs38}and a refrigerator full of spoiled wedding shrimp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.84,0:10:03.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小心你的背后\N{\fs38}Watch your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.22,0:10:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去洗手吧 宝贝\N{\fs38}And wash your arm, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么迟到\N{\fs38}Why are you late?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么律师先生要召开紧急会议\N{\fs38}Why did Mr. Lawyer call an emergency meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.69,0:10:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是Vonda干的好事吗\N{\fs38}Did Vonda do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.15,0:10:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Titus 你放她鸽子的把戏\N{\fs38}Titus, the way you bailed on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.90,0:10:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在别人身上用过吗\N{\fs38}have you ever done that to anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一张山姆古迪商店的信用卡没还\N{\fs38}A Sam Goody credit card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:22.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放弃了我的大学橄榄球奖学金\N{\fs38}My college football scholarship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.49,0:10:25.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还离开了长得比我帅的表弟 大傻瓜Darius\N{\fs38}My cousin who got handsomer than me-- Stupid Darius.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 我不会付钱给这个律师\N{\fs38}Also, I'm not gonna pay this lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.37,0:10:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我有一个好消息 一个坏消息\N{\fs38}Well, I've got good news, and I've got bad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏消息是 Instagram删除了我的账号\N{\fs38}The bad news is, Instagram canceled my account
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.75,0:10:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,理由是我缺乏兴趣\N{\fs38}due to lack of interest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.13,0:10:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好消息是\N{\fs38}The good news is that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.09,0:10:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早在2008年 Ronald Wilkerson就已经在法律上被宣布死亡\N{\fs38}in 2008, Ronald Wilkerson was declared legally dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是她宣布的\N{\fs38}by this woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.89,0:10:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他已经失踪十年了\N{\fs38}He'd been missing ten years.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:47.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他饮食那么不健康 十年都给多了\N{\fs38}With his diet, I was being generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够犀利\N{\fs38}Sick burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.56,0:10:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而\N{\fs38}However,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.56,0:10:51.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不仅领取了Wilkerson先生的社保收入\N{\fs38}you did collect Mr. Wilkerson's Social Security earnings,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且获取了他为自己双腿投保\N{\fs38}as well as the money from an insurance policy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所得的收入\N{\fs38}he took out on his legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.73,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Mary Hart: 美国电视女主持人 为美腿投保百万美金
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那时受到了Mary Hart的启发\N{\fs38}I was inspired by Mary Hart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.82,0:11:00.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为我的资产投保\N{\fs38}to insure my assets at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.11,0:11:02.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为"Ronald Wilkerson"已经死了\N{\fs38}So because "Ronald Wilkerson" is dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.26,0:11:03.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你不能起诉他 Brooks女士 \N{\fs38}Ms. Brooks, you can't sue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.03,0:11:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上 你还欠他大约500美元\N{\fs38}As a matter of fact, you may owe him about $500.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.91,0:11:08.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 什么  - 什么\N{\fs38}- What? - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧 我认为我们的会议结束了\N{\fs38}Well, I think we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.58,0:11:10.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,砰 贱人\N{\fs38}Boom, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.58,0:11:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜拜\N{\fs38}Bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.54,0:11:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跟我作对\N{\fs38}I am not the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,报纸的幽默版块见 乡巴佬\N{\fs38}See you in the funny papers, Country Mouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.63,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Jennife Love Hewitt: 女演员 曾出演美剧<鬼语者>\NPhil Rizzuto: 已故职业棒球明星 曾给贷款品牌做代言人\N
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你最好打电话给Jennifer Love Hewitt和Phil Rizzuto吧\N{\fs38}You better call Jennifer Love Hewitt and Phil Rizzuto,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你欠鬼魂的钱\N{\fs38}because you owe a ghost money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.43,0:11:28.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝你好运 Kimmy\N{\fs38}Good luck with that, Kimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lillian 你觉得Titus会像对待Vonda那样\N{\fs38}Lillian, do you think Titus would ever do to us
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对待我们吗\N{\fs38}what he did to Vonda?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把饼干嚼碎 然后在舞会结束后假装吐在我们身上\N{\fs38}Chew up crackers and pretend to throw up on us after prom
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以此来避免跟别人上床吗\N{\fs38}to get out of sex?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以预见 没错\N{\fs38}I could see it happening, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是谁在乎呢\N{\fs38}But who cares?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们出去浪\N{\fs38}We're going out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.33,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,讽刺美国国家安全局监听民众电话的行径
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.49,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们拿到的电话号码会比国安局的还要多\N{\fs38}We're gonna get more phone numbers than the NSA.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政治手段\N{\fs38}Political!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 没错\N{\fs38}Yes! Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们享受人生\N{\fs38}Let's go life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 我要进里面买点东西\N{\fs38}Oh, wait, I need something in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去内衣那边看看\N{\fs38}Oh, I'll be in intimates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨 我要一盒杀虫药\N{\fs38}Hi, I need a box of silverfish poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有了 抱歉 女士 那家伙买了最后一盒\N{\fs38}No, sorry, ma'am. That guy's buy the last one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.26,0:12:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kimmy{\fs38}\NKimmy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.47,0:12:06.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dong{\fs38}\NDong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.10,0:12:10.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起来不错\N{\fs38}You look well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.60,0:12:12.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你\N{\fs38}It's so nice to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想见你\N{\fs38}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老婆怎么样了\N{\fs38}How is your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是Sonja吗\N{\fs38}Still Sonja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.56,0:12:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 谢谢\N{\fs38}Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.31,0:12:20.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和Sonja明天要请人吃早午餐\N{\fs38}Sonja and I are having people over for brunch tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是蠹虫把我们的毛巾都咬烂了\N{\fs38}and the silverfish ate all our towels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的英语说得真溜\N{\fs38}Wow, your English is getting really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs38}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.11,0:12:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再也没有你来帮我学英语了\N{\fs38}I didn't have you to help me anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:28.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我看了很多集\N{\fs38}so I started watching a lot of...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:31.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,<与卡戴珊姐妹同行>\N{\fs38}Keeping Up with the Kardashians.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊 有效果了\N{\fs38}Well, it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真好\N{\fs38}Aw, you're sweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.83,0:12:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dong{\fs38}\NDong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.21,0:12:36.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs38}My God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.54,0:12:38.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你应该跟我们一起去滑旱冰\N{\fs38}You should come roller-skating with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 Lillian 不行\N{\fs38}What? Lillian, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道三个人一起你就不会滑了\N{\fs38}Everyone knows you can't skate as a threesies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴\N{\fs38}Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,运气好的话 我们可能会来个四人行\N{\fs38}As luck would have it, we'll be a foursome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.93,0:12:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚碰见我的老情人Bobby了\N{\fs38}I just ran into my old flame, Bobby.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 你们好\N{\fs38}Okay, hi-hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:58.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想Dong该回去他老婆身边了 Lillian\N{\fs38}I think Dong probably needs to get back to his wife, Lillian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.31,0:13:01.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实 Sonja去上比克拉姆热瑜伽课了\N{\fs38}Actually, Sonja's at her Bikram hot yoga class,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.27,0:13:03.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且在释放杀虫药之后的7个小时里\N{\fs38}and I do have to stay out of the apartment
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不能进屋\N{\fs38}for seven hours after I set off the silverfish bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.24,0:13:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以呢 那提议太棒了\N{\fs38}So, yeah, that sounds amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美\N{\fs38}Well, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来个四人行\N{\fs38}We'll be a foursome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\fs38}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想要这个\N{\fs38}I want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要才怪\N{\fs38}Like you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.38,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说得对 我是错的\N{\fs38}You're right. I'm wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.55,0:13:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*你可以感受它的存在*\N{\fs38}*You can feel it*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*它会保佑我们*\N{\fs38}*It protects us*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.55,0:13:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*我扭 我扭 我扭扭扭*\N{\fs38}*Boogie oogie oogie oogie.*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.89,0:13:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*向玉米之神祈祷*\N{\fs38}*Pray to the corn god*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.51,0:13:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,*他是电动玉米*\N{\fs38}*He's corn-lectric*
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.27,0:13:36.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要跳\N{\fs38}Why are you doing the...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白人傻瓜的\N{\fs38}White idiot
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.68,0:13:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼舞蹈\N{\fs38}wedding dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.73,0:13:42.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白人傻瓜\N{\fs38}White idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.81,0:13:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的玉米之神啊\N{\fs38}Oh, my corn god.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早午饭 对吗\N{\fs38}So a brunch, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.74,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Frasier: 美剧<欢乐一家亲>的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.28,0:13:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Frasier那样高雅\N{\fs38}That's Frasier fancy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.82,0:13:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只是为了给移民局官员留下好印象\N{\fs38}It's just to impress the immigration officer.
