Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实不曾想要伤害Vonda Jeanne\N{\fs38}I sure didn't want to hurt Vonda Jeanne.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕面对她\N{\fs38}I was scared to face her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是她不愿接受我的道歉怎么办\N{\fs38}What if she wouldn't accept my apology?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.64,0:19:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴 Ronald 你这个蠢货\N{\fs38}Shut up, Ronald, you nerd.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.81,0:19:12.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了吧\N{\fs38}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就知道\N{\fs38}I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得接受Ronald的存在 Titus\N{\fs38}You need to embrace your Ronald, Titus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fs38}For why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.90,0:19:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了我 现在我就是你的Vonda\N{\fs38}For me. I'm your Vonda now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.11,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道你会不会打包跑路\N{\fs38}How do I know you won't just pack up and run away from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能我不会啊\N{\fs38}Because I probably won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在能让我安静地享用火腿蛤蜊披萨了吗\N{\fs38}Now, can I please eat my ham and clam pizza in peace?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.20,0:19:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对\N{\fs38}That's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这配料不对\N{\fs38}Those toppings are wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.29,0:19:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我同意 先给我20分钟\N{\fs38}I will agree with you in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没事 不是吗\N{\fs38}But it doesn't matter, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.58,0:19:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是纽约\N{\fs38}'Cause this is New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.96,0:19:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每个人都在道德上是相对的\N{\fs38}where everyone's moral relatives.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.21,0:19:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只要点份深盘火腿蛤蜊披萨\N{\fs38}Just order a deep-dish ham/clam,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.42,0:19:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某个死变态就会给你做\N{\fs38}and some sicko will make it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.21,0:19:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得让你知道我没点这个\N{\fs38}I'll have you know I didn't order these.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.67,0:19:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我捡的\N{\fs38}I found them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.09,0:19:44.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这个城市里唯一一个\N{\fs38}Am I the only person in this city
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.13,0:19:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不那么随便的人吗\N{\fs38}who doesn't just do whatevs whenevs?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干他妈的糖\N{\fs38}Well, fudge that sugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让它见鬼去吧\N{\fs38}Fudge it to heck,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.60,0:19:52.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长着一千根小鸡鸡的魔鬼\N{\fs38}where a demon with a thousand wee-wees
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.31,0:19:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会干死它\N{\fs38}fudges it forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要毁了Dong的早午饭\N{\fs38}I'm crashing Dong's brunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在这儿热得跟个印第安人一样\N{\fs38}I'm sweating like an Indian in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 我可以这么说\N{\fs38}It's okay. I can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以说\N{\fs38}I can say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Jackie Lynn 圆环象征着团结\N{\fs38}Jackie Lynn, the hoop symbolizes unity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出现幻觉了\N{\fs38}I'm visioning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:21.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们没有那么多的钱\N{\fs38}We have so little money as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.46,0:20:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家房子在那边 蠢货\N{\fs38}Your house is that way, dummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你属于另一个部族了\N{\fs38}You belong to a different tribe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我扭 我扭 我扭扭扭\N{\fs38}Boogie oogie, oogie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉米之神 你真是个电动玉米\N{\fs38}Corn god. You are corn-lectric.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴上你的隐形眼镜\N{\fs38}Just use your contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的人脉联系在曼哈顿\N{\fs38}Your connections are back in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在曼哈顿\N{\fs38}In Manhattan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.31,0:20:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么还只是个物品\N{\fs38}How am I still a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 联系  - 回曼哈顿\N{\fs38}- Connections. - Back in Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.36,0:20:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曲棍球是我们发明的\N{\fs38}Lacrosse is our thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐形眼镜 隐形眼镜\N{\fs38}Contacts, contacts, contacts.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道我该做什么了\N{\fs38}I know what I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kimmy\N{\fs38}Kimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.95,0:20:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是GED课上的Sonja\N{\fs38}It's Sonja from GED class?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡通版Anastasia公主就是关于我的\N{\fs38}Also, the cartoon Anastasia is about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.08,0:20:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了 Sonja\N{\fs38}Of course. Sonja.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.08,0:20:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs38}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.33,0:21:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kimmy是我们最好的朋友\N{\fs38}Kimmy is our best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦\N{\fs38}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:04.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你当时参加了他们的婚礼吗\N{\fs38}Were you at their wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.42,0:21:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来想去的\N{\fs38}Well, I wanted to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:07.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可这两只爱情鸟私奔了\N{\fs38}but these two lovebirds eloped.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.68,0:21:09.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天可不是爱情鸟哟\N{\fs38}I'm not a bird today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kimmy{\fs38}\NKimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:12.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 你在干  - 听着\N{\fs38}- What are you-- - Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要和你私下聊聊\N{\fs38}I need to talk to you in private.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.93,0:21:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这儿干嘛\N{\fs38}What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.27,0:21:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我们昨晚过得很开心 对吗\N{\fs38}Look it, we had fun last night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.40,0:21:20.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 不过后来就很诡异了\N{\fs38}Yeah. But then things got weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.06,0:21:22.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像Kourtney把母乳喷到\N{\fs38}Like when Kourtney squirted
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.40,0:21:24.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kim的牛皮癣上那样诡异\N{\fs38}her breast milk on Kim's psoriasis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会知道这个\N{\fs38}Why do I know about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.78,0:21:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点来了\N{\fs38}Here's the thing:
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.90,0:21:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活中有些灰色地带\N{\fs38}there are gray areas in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.53,0:21:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sonja的牛皮癣面积超大\N{\fs38}Sonja's is enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.91,0:21:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我知道我们都想做对的事\N{\fs38}Look, I know we both want to do the right thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.99,0:21:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但同样我也迫不及待让我的生活\N{\fs38}but I also can't wait anymore for my life to...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.79,0:21:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 等下  - 开始\N{\fs38}- Stop. - ...start.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.70,0:21:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉的蠹虫\N{\fs38}Dead silverfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.54,0:21:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得这打虫药挺管用的\N{\fs38}I guess the poison's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.42,0:21:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 现在又有一只在你头发里了\N{\fs38}Oh, now there's one in your hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.50,0:21:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着\N{\fs38}Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.98,0:21:58.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kimmy 不\N{\fs38}Kimmy, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.27,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能这么做\N{\fs38}We can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.31,0:22:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着 我来自中西部\N{\fs38}Look, I'm from the Midwest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂婚姻的圣洁\N{\fs38}I believe in the sanctity of marr--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.52,0:22:05.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蠹虫\N{\fs38}Silverfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.28,0:22:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我想和你亲热 这样我才不会崩溃\N{\fs38}But I also want to rub my mouth on your mouth so I don't boof.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.28,0:22:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下\N{\fs38}Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.49,0:22:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要的不过是不被驱逐出境 就这样\N{\fs38}All I want is not to be deported. That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.74,0:22:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那昨晚怎么回事\N{\fs38}What about last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.16,0:22:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚是个错误\N{\fs38}Last night was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.70,0:22:16.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Lillian的头发看起来像面条一样\N{\fs38}Lillian's hair looked like noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.45,0:22:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被缠住了\N{\fs38}I got caught up in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果移民署的那位女士也很爱滑旱冰呢\N{\fs38}What if the immigration lady was also super into roller-skating?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.87,0:22:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能会失去一切\N{\fs38}I could have lost everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.17,0:22:24.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- 但是  - 我觉得你该走了\N{\fs38}- But-- - I think you should leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许两年后再见吧\N{\fs38}Maybe I'll see you in two years, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.31,0:22:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Titus 你在干嘛呢\N{\fs38}Titus, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:47.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 只不过吵了一架你就要走吗\N{\fs38}Wow, so one fight and you're out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.90,0:22:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了我的工作 男朋友\N{\fs38}I've lost my job, my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.07,0:22:51.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢的发带 现在连你也要走了吗\N{\fs38}my favorite scrunchie, and now you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.07,0:22:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想说这个 Kimmy\N{\fs38}I don't want to talk about this, Kimmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.07,0:22:56.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是小题大做\N{\fs38}I'm being dramatical.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.37,0:22:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 你走\N{\fs38}Fine. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.12,0:23:01.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次逃避你的问题吧\N{\fs38}Just run away from your problems... again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.12,0:23:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能永远逃避问题的 Titus\N{\fs38}You can't keep running away forever, Titus.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.71,0:23:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢 我要紧紧跟着你\N{\fs38}Oh, I will keep following you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.46,0:23:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是对的\N{\fs38}You know I'm right!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的罪恶感会伴随你一生一世\N{\fs38}Your guilt will chase you wherever you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你逃不了的 Titus\N{\fs38}You can't escape, Titus!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去比洛克西的火车开了吗\N{\fs38}Has the train to Biloxi left yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没 晚点两个小时\N{\fs38}Nope. It's running two hours late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.31,0:23:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vonda{\fs38}\NVonda!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs38}Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.19,0:23:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下 Vonda\N{\fs38}Wait. Vonda?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.28,0:23:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊 谢天谢地车还没开\N{\fs38}Boy, good thing the train was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.32,0:23:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哈 你觉得我们仅仅只是列车公司吗\N{\fs38}Ha. You think we're a train company?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们故意延迟发车的\N{\fs38}We run late on purpose
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.53,0:23:40.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样人们就能以一种浪漫的方式找到彼此了\N{\fs38}so people can find each other in romantical fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:42.41,注释,NTP,0,0,0,,Amtrak: 美国国家铁路客运公司\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美铁 为爱而生\N{\fs38}Amtrak... is for lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.54,0:23:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Phillip{\fs38}\NPhillip?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.42,0:23:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sheila{\fs38}\NSheila.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.55,0:23:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vonda 我很抱歉\N{\fs38}Vonda... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.14,0:24:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们之间的友谊那么深切真实\N{\fs38}The friendship we had was deep and real,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.14,0:24:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不该以那种方式丢下你\N{\fs38}and I should've never abandoned you that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能这就是为什么我不找你的缘故吧\N{\fs38}Maybe that's why I never called,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.27,0:24:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怕知道我伤你多深\N{\fs38}'cause I was afraid to hear how much I had hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.19,0:24:11.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过如果你还肯要我\N{\fs38}But if you'll have me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.07,0:24:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意做你的朋友\N{\fs38}I'd like to be your friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.70,0:24:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不打炮\N{\fs38}without benefits.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.24,0:24:16.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意\N{\fs38}I'd like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.33,0:24:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在 我还想还你一些\N{\fs38}And now, I'd like to pay you back
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.75,0:24:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我欠你的东西\N{\fs38}a little of what I owe you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.92,0:24:35.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女士们先生们\N{\fs38}Ladies and gentlemen,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次\N{\fs38}for the first time anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.18,0:24:42.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vonda Jeanne Brooks\N{\fs38}Ms. and Mr. Vonda Jeanne Brooks
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.89,0:24:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和Titus Ronald Wilkerson-Andromedon-Yoshimura\N{\fs38}and Titus Ronald Wilkerson-Andromedon-Yoshimura.
